Source: zscaler-mcp
Section: misc
Priority: optional
Maintainer: Docker Hardened Images <dhi@docker.com>
Build-Depends: debhelper-compat (= 13)
Standards-Version: 4.7.0
Homepage: https://github.com/zscaler/zscaler-mcp-server

Package: zscaler-mcp
Architecture: any
Depends: ${misc:Depends}, python3
Description: Zscaler MCP server
 Model Context Protocol server that connects AI assistants and LLM-powered IDEs
 to the Zscaler Zero Trust Exchange platform. The Python runtime is supplied by
 the consuming image; this package ships the application virtual environment
 under /opt/zscaler-mcp, exposing the zscaler-mcp console command over the MCP
 stdio transport.
